"MAVEN ,ANT, GRADLE" used for java based projects , ".Net" use "visual studio" as build tool

Maven is a "Java based project" , so If you want to run maven you need to install java as pre-requisite.

Open:
1.https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi

click on 
windows install zip file

https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi
https://dlcdn.apache.org/maven/maven-3/3.8.4/binaries/apache-maven-3.8.4-bin.zip

install this maven and copy to 
C:\Devops_softwares\Maven-3.8

Once done 

2.#Add path to environment variables
Search for control panel --> advnace system setting --> environment variables --> system varialbe --> new 
#Name: MAVEN_HOME 
#Path: C:\Devops_softwares\Maven-3.8\apache-maven-3.8.4

Once add MAVEN_HOME VARIABLE update, Update path on "Path" variable till /bin
#Path: 
#add : C:\Devops_softwares\Maven-3.8\apache-maven-3.8.4\bin

click on Ok 

Open new CMD and check maven version using

Enter:
3.mvn 
  mvn -version

C:\Users\vinod>mvn -version
